cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.CL 

This paper is about video summarization, which involves analyzing and processing visual content. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses probabilistic modeling and learning algorithms, which are relevant to machine learning and statistics. This suggests that the paper could also belong to cs.MM (Multimedia), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.LG (Machine Learning), or cs.CL (Computation and Language). However, since the focus is on visual content, cs.CV is the most likely category.
